ct into the Tonnage Tax scheme as a group of companies. 2014-15 data is currently unavailable and will only be made available from Autumn 2017.</p>","Battersea","Jane Ellison","63121 ; 63125 ; 63129 ; 63147","2017-02-09T16:03:21.47Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/685430/answer","Biography information for Jane Ellison","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/685430/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/685430/answer",,,,,,,,"14","Treasury","CaTreasury","2017-02-06","Business Premises Renovation Allowance","1","House of Commons","To ask Mr Chancellor of the Exchequer, how many (a) people and (b) businesses received the Business Premises Renovation Allowance in (i) 2013-14 and (ii) 2014-15.","false","Biography information for Rebecca Long Bailey","Salford and Eccles","Rebecca Long Bailey","63133"
